<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wmhmạ tkwny ḥṣynẗ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (wmhmạ tkwny ḥṣynẗ rạḥ tqʿy yạ ạ̉swạr
 wmhmạ tkwn qdrạtk wạtẖqyn fy ạ̹lh jbạr)2
 rạfʿyn rạyạt ạlgẖlbẗ wʿlạmẗ ạlạntṣạr
 (ạ̉ʿẓm mn mntṣryn ạ̹ḥnạ byswʿ ạlbạr)2
 2- (hạnlf ạ̹ḥnạ ḥwạlyky whạnnsy̱ kl ʿyạn
 whạnhtf bạsm mlyknạ wnsẖwfk bạlạ̹ymạn)2
 tḥt ạlrjlyn mndạsẗ mhmạ ṭạl ạlzmạn
 (ạ̉ʿẓm mn mntṣryn ạ̹ḥnạ fy sẖkẖṣ ạlḥnạn)2
 3- (lạ gẖrwrk dwh hyfḍl wʿnạdk msẖ hạydwm
 hạyjylk ywm whạtqʿy̱ dh ạ̉kyd rạḥ yyjy ạlywm)2
 wjnwdk thrb kẖạyfẗ tkẖrj mn swr mhdwm
 (ạ̉ʿẓm mn mntṣryn wmlykk ṣạr mhzwm)2
 4- (rạḥ tbqy̱ ạlạ̉swạr dẖkry̱ wsẖhạdẗ ʿẓymẗ lsẖkẖṣk
 wsẖʿbk yfrḥ byk wydẖyʿ ạ̉frạḥh bnṣrk)2
 kl ạtkạlnạ ʿlyk wslạm qlwbnạ fy ṣkẖrk
 (ạ̉ʿẓm mn mntṣryn mn ywm mạ ksạnạ brk)2</lyrics>
<author>sạmḥ ʿbdh, bhyr ạ̹dwạrd</author>
<hymn_number>49</hymn_number>
</song>